COPY public.awards (id, name, alias, basics_description, details_story, details_awarded_date, details_awarded_location, assets_thumbnail_id, assets_candid_id, assets_video_id, generate_slug, slug, updated_at, created_at) FROM stdin;
3	Porsche Cup Debut Victory - Estoril 2025	porsche-cup-debut-victory-2025	Victory in AF Motorsport's first competitive Porsche Cup event at the 2025 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica season opener at Estoril. The achievement marked the team's successful transition to Porsche one-make competition.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The debut victory came in Race 2 of the Estoril season opener, with André Fernandes converting a front-row starting position into a controlled lights-to-flag performance after an early overtake for the lead. The result provided immediate validation of the team's preparation and the competitiveness of AF Motorsport's Porsche program.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The victory represented the culmination of extensive preparation including personnel development, technical partnership establishment, and pre-season testing. Achieving success in the first competitive outing established momentum that carried through the debut Porsche campaign.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2025-03-23 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E610000048E17A14AE47444016FBCBEEC98324C0	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-cup-debut-victory---estoril-2025	2026-04-10 10:41:18.942+05:30	2026-04-09 21:14:22.431+05:30
1	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica Championship Third Place 2025	psci-championship-third-2025	Third place overall in the 2025 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica driver championship, representing AF Motorsport's highest championship finish in its debut Porsche campaign. The result validated the team's preparation standards and competitive methodology against established Porsche competitors.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " The 2025 championship campaign exceeded pre-season expectations, delivering three race victories, nine total podium finishes, and third place in the final championship standings. The result represented the culmination of AF Motorsport's methodical preparation and the team's successful transition to Porsche one-make competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Key performances included a breakthrough victory at the Estoril season opener, a dominant win at the Portimão summer round, and a season-ending victory at the Estoril finale that secured the championship bronze position. The campaign demonstrated consistent competitiveness across varying circuit types and conditions.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The achievement carried additional significance as the highest championship finish by a Portuguese team in the unified Iberian series, establishing AF Motorsport's credentials within the regional Porsche Motorsport ecosystem.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2025-10-19 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000002D211FF46CB62D40BF7D1D38678424C0	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-championship-third-place-2025	2026-04-10 10:41:46.77+05:30	2026-04-09 21:11:50.586+05:30
5	CPV Class Victory - Estoril 2024	cpv-class-victory-estoril-2024	Class victory in the Campeonato de Portugal de Velocidade at Estoril, achieved prior to AF Motorsport's full-time transition to Porsche competition. The result demonstrated the team's competitive capability in national championship competition.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The CPV class victory at Estoril in 2024 represented AF Motorsport's final major achievement in Portuguese national championship competition before the full transition to Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica. The result validated the team's operational standards and competitive preparation methodology.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The victory contributed to the team's development trajectory, providing competitive experience and confidence that informed the subsequent Porsche program. Success in the multi-class national championship environment demonstrated the team's adaptability and race execution capability.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2024-06-15 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000EC51B81E851B434021B07268916D22C0	\N	\N	\N	f	cpv-class-victory---estoril-2024	2026-04-10 10:40:52.63+05:30	2026-04-09 21:16:35.478+05:30
4	PSCI Rookie of the Year Nomination 2025	psci-rookie-nomination-2025	Official nomination for Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica Rookie of the Year honors, recognizing the most impressive debut season performance in the championship. The nomination acknowledged AF Motorsport's immediate competitiveness and professional approach in its first Porsche campaign.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " The Rookie of the Year nomination recognized AF Motorsport's achievement in transitioning directly to competitive front-running performance in its debut Porsche season. The nomination criteria considered race results, championship position, professionalism, and contribution to the championship's competitive environment.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The recognition from Porsche Motorsport and championship organizers validated the team's approach to preparation and competition, establishing AF Motorsport as a respected entrant within the Iberian Porsche community.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2025-10-19 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000AAF1D24D6220444000000000008024C0	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-rookie-of-the-year-nomination-2025	2026-04-10 10:41:04.024+05:30	2026-04-09 21:15:33.247+05:30
2	Estoril Circuit Track Record - Porsche 992 GT3 Cup	estoril-track-record-992-2025	Official track record for Porsche 992 GT3 Cup cars at Autódromo do Estoril, established during the 2025 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica season finale. The record time of 1:30.156 represents the fastest competitive lap recorded by a 992-generation Porsche Cup car at the circuit.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The track record was established during Race 2 of the 2025 season finale at Estoril, with the time recorded on lap 7 of the 18-lap contest. The achievement demonstrated both outright performance and the ability to extract maximum pace under race conditions with tire degradation and fuel load considerations.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The record held particular significance for AF Motorsport as the team's home circuit, validating the setup development work conducted at the Estoril facility and the team's deep understanding of the circuit's characteristics. The benchmark time remains the reference for Porsche Cup performance at the historic Portuguese venue.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2025-10-19 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000002D211FF46C96434000000000008022C0	\N	\N	\N	f	estoril-circuit-track-record---porsche-992-gt3-cup	2026-04-10 10:41:32.534+05:30	2026-04-09 21:12:57.654+05:30
6	André Fernandes P2 GT Class Murça 2026	andre-fernandes-p2-murca-2026	Second place finish in GT class for André Fernandes at the Rampa Porca de Murça 2026 hillclimb, driving the Porsche 991.2 GT3 R.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " In his debut competitive appearance in the Porsche 991.2 GT3 R, André Fernandes secured a podium finish at the prestigious Rampa Porca de Murça. The second-place result in the highly competitive GT class validated both driver performance and AF Motorsport's preparation standards.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The achievement carried additional significance as Fernandes balanced driving duties with overall team leadership throughout the event. The podium demonstrated that the dual role of team principal and competitive driver remains viable when supported by strong organizational structure and personnel.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-29 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008FC2F5285CDF414023DBF97E6A1C25C0	\N	\N	\N	f	andr-fernandes-p2-gt-class-mura-2026	2026-04-10 16:25:40.578+05:30	2026-04-10 16:25:40.578+05:30
7	Pipo Massa Race 1 Victory Barcelona Winter Series	pipo-massa-barcelona-victory-award	First place overall in Cup 2 class and first European race victory for Pipo Massa at the GT Winter Series Barcelona finale.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pipo Massa claimed his first European race victory in dominant fashion at the Barcelona Winter Series finale, mastering challenging wet conditions to secure the win by a narrow but controlled 0.637-second margin. The victory represented a significant milestone in the young Brazilian's development and validated AF Motorsport's driver development approach.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The performance demonstrated Pipo's growing racecraft, including wet-weather car control, pace management under pressure, and the mental composure to execute when victory was within reach. The award recognized both the achievement and the potential it suggests for continued progression.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-14 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000F4FDD478E9C64140ACADD85F764F22C0	\N	\N	\N	f	pipo-massa-race-1-victory-barcelona-winter-series	2026-04-10 16:27:15.196+05:30	2026-04-10 16:27:15.196+05:30
8	Pipo Massa First European Victory Recognition	pipo-massa-first-european-win-award	Special recognition commemorating Pipo Massa's breakthrough first victory on European soil, achieved in the GT Winter Series at Barcelona.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "This special recognition commemorates Pipo Massa's first European race victory—a milestone in any young driver's career that carries particular significance given the Massa family legacy in motorsport. Achieved in challenging wet conditions at Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya, the victory demonstrated both natural talent and the effectiveness of Pipo's development program.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The award celebrates not just the result but the journey: countless hours of simulator work, data analysis sessions, physical preparation, and the resilience required to compete at the professional level. For AF Motorsport, Pipo's victory validates the team's commitment to developing complete racing professionals.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-14 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000A01A2FDD24C64140E7FBA9F1D26D22C0	\N	\N	\N	f	pipo-massa-first-european-victory-recognition	2026-04-10 16:29:25.865+05:30	2026-04-10 16:29:25.865+05:30
9	Rogério Grotta Fastest Lap Portimão Debut	rogerio-grotta-fastest-lap-portimao	Fastest lap award for Rogério Grotta in his debut drive in the Porsche 991.2 GT3 R at Portimão, achieved in challenging wet conditions.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "n extraordinary circumstances—first time driving a Porsche 991.2 GT3 R, first time racing at the demanding Portimão circuit, and doing so in wet conditions—Rogério Grotta set the fastest lap of the race. The achievement demonstrated exceptional adaptability, natural car control, and the ability to extract performance regardless of circumstances.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The fastest lap served notice of Grotta's potential in European GT competition and validated AF Motorsport's decision to bring the Brazilian talent into the team's endurance program. The award recognizes both the statistical achievement and the remarkable context in which it was earned.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-08 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000007593180456FE4140925CFE43FA6D22C0	\N	\N	\N	f	rogrio-grotta-fastest-lap-portimo-debut	2026-04-10 16:31:31.592+05:30	2026-04-10 16:31:31.591+05:30
\.


