4	André Fernandes Birthday Team Celebration 2026	fernandes-birthday-team-gathering-2026	Informal team gathering combining celebration of André Fernandes's birthday with mid-season team bonding ahead of the championship's second half. The relaxed social event strengthened personal connections within the team during the brief mid-season break.	private	2026-08-15 23:30:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000C58F31772D594340107A36AB3ED722C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The mid-season calendar break provided opportunity for AF Motorsport personnel to gather away from the competitive environment and strengthen the personal bonds that underpin team cohesion. The gathering, coinciding with André Fernandes's birthday, offered relaxed social interaction that contrasted with the intense focus of race weekends.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The informal celebration acknowledged the human element of motorsport—the relationships, trust, and mutual respect that enable effective collaboration under pressure. Team members and their families enjoyed an evening of Portuguese hospitality with the Atlantic coastline providing a fitting backdrop for reflection on the season's first half achievements and anticipation of the championship conclusion ahead.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    Such gatherings have become an important element of AF Motorsport's team culture, recognizing that sustainable success requires investment in the personal connections that sustain motivation and commitment through the inevitable challenges of competitive motorsport.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	andr-fernandes-birthday-team-celebration-2026	2026-04-10 10:42:43.837+05:30	2026-04-10 00:49:13.867+05:30
2	AF Motorsport 2025 Championship Podium Celebration	afm-2025-championship-podium-celebration	Formal and informal celebrations marking AF Motorsport's achievement of third place in the 2025 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship standings. The celebration acknowledged the team's successful debut Porsche campaign and the collective effort that delivered championship success.	private	2025-10-20 00:30:00+05:30	0101000020E610000012143FC6DC9D4240151DC9E53F4421C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The conclusion of the 2025 season at Portimão brought together AF Motorsport personnel, partners, and supporters for a celebration of the team's championship podium achievement. The evening combined the formal recognition of the championship awards ceremony with an intimate team gathering that acknowledged every individual's contribution to the season's success.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The championship podium represented far more than a competitive result—it validated AF Motorsport's preparation methodology, operational standards, and the collective commitment of every team member. The celebration provided opportunity for reflection on the journey from the organization's founding through to establishing credible Porsche competition credentials.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    Partners joined the celebration, reinforcing the collaborative nature of the achievement and the shared investment in AF Motorsport's development. The evening strengthened relationships and created momentum for the continued progression into the 2026 season and beyond.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-2025-championship-podium-celebration	2026-04-10 10:43:19.66+05:30	2026-04-10 00:47:34.681+05:30
6	End of Season Appreciation Dinner 2026	afm-end-of-season-dinner-2026	Formal appreciation dinner honoring AF Motorsport personnel, partners, and supporters following the conclusion of the 2026 championship season. The celebration recognized individual and collective contributions to the season's achievements.	private	2026-11-08 00:30:00+05:30	0101000020E61000004DF38E53745C434065AA6054524722C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The conclusion of the 2026 season was marked by a formal appreciation dinner bringing together everyone who had contributed to AF Motorsport's campaign. The evening provided opportunity for leadership to personally recognize the efforts of team members whose dedication often occurs away from public attention—the mechanics whose preparation ensures reliability, the engineers whose analysis extracts performance, and the support personnel whose organization enables everything else.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    Partners were honored for their essential contribution, with the recognition extending beyond financial support to encompass the collaborative relationships that enhance the team's capability and reach. The evening balanced formal acknowledgment with genuine appreciation, reinforcing the organizational culture that values every individual's contribution to collective achievement.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The dinner also served as transition point, closing the chapter on the completed season while building momentum and commitment for the campaign ahead. For AF Motorsport, such gatherings represent investment in the organizational fabric that sustains performance through the cycles of competitive motorsport.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	end-of-season-appreciation-dinner-2026	2026-04-10 10:42:19.7+05:30	2026-04-10 00:51:10.734+05:30
1	AF Motorsport Maiden Porsche Victory Celebration 2025	afm-maiden-porsche-victory-2025	Spontaneous celebration following AF Motorsport's historic first Porsche victory at the 2025 Estoril season opener. The celebration captured the genuine emotion and significance of the team's breakthrough achievement in its debut Porsche campaign.	private	2025-03-23 22:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008048BF7D1D604340448B6CE7FBC922C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The moments following the checkered flag of Race 2 at Estoril produced an outpouring of genuine emotion across the AF Motorsport garage. Team personnel embraced as confirmation of victory was received, with mechanics, engineers, and support staff sharing in the achievement that validated months of preparation and years of organizational development.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The celebration was spontaneous and authentic—champagne sprayed across race suits, tearful embraces between long-time team members, and the traditional Portuguese victory song echoing through the Estoril pit lane. For André Fernandes, the victory represented the culmination of a journey from national competitor to Porsche race winner and the realization of a vision to build a team capable of competing successfully at the Iberian championship level.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The Estoril circuit staff, many of whom had watched AF Motorsport develop from its earliest days, joined the celebration, adding local significance to the achievement at the team's home circuit. The victory established a new benchmark for the organization and created a shared memory that strengthened team bonds for the challenges ahead.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-maiden-porsche-victory-celebration-2025	2026-04-10 10:43:46.672+05:30	2026-04-10 00:46:53.588+05:30
5	Estoril Victory Anniversary Recognition 2026	estoril-victory-anniversary-2026	Informal recognition of the one-year anniversary of AF Motorsport's maiden Porsche victory at Estoril. The moment of acknowledgment during the 2026 season opener weekend honored the significance of the breakthrough achievement.	private	2026-03-23 17:30:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008048BF7D1D604340448B6CE7FBC922C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "During the 2026 Estoril season opener weekend, the AF Motorsport team paused briefly to acknowledge the one-year anniversary of the organization's first Porsche victory at the same circuit. The moment was understated but meaningful—a brief gathering of team personnel who had been present for the historic achievement, sharing memories of the breakthrough that had validated the team's direction.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The recognition served as a reminder of progress made and a touchstone for the organization's identity. From maiden victory to established championship contender in twelve months, the anniversary provided perspective on AF Motorsport's development trajectory while reinforcing the values and approach that had delivered success.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    For newer team members who had joined since the victory, the moment provided connection to team heritage and an understanding of the foundations upon which current ambitions are built.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	estoril-victory-anniversary-recognition-2026	2026-04-10 10:42:31.689+05:30	2026-04-10 00:50:06.862+05:30
3	AF Motorsport Season Launch Celebration 2026	afm-season-launch-2026	Official celebration marking the launch of AF Motorsport's 2026 competitive program and the unveiling of the team's new season livery. The event brought together partners, media, and team personnel for an evening of anticipation and commitment to the season ahead.	public	2026-03-01 01:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008048BF7D1D604340448B6CE7FBC922C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The 2026 season launch celebration transformed the AF Motorsport workshop into an elegant venue for partner appreciation and season anticipation. Guests were welcomed into the team's operational heart, with the newly-liveried Porsche 992 GT3 Cup cars presented under dramatic lighting that emphasized the striking visual identity developed for the new campaign.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    The evening program included formal presentations outlining the team's 2026 ambitions, recognition of continuing and new partners, and the opportunity for guests to engage directly with team personnel and equipment. The celebration balanced professional presentation with authentic motorsport atmosphere, reinforcing AF Motorsport's positioning as a credible and ambitious organization.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "    For the team, the celebration marked the transition from preparation to execution and the collective commitment to converting potential into performance across the championship season ahead.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-season-launch-celebration-2026	2026-04-10 10:42:58.169+05:30	2026-04-10 00:48:21.613+05:30
7	St. Patrick's Day 2026 Celebration	st-patricks-day-2026-celebration	AF Motorsport's public St. Patrick's Day celebration across social media channels, engaging the global motorsport community with Irish-themed content.	public	2026-03-17 14:30:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008048BF7D1D604340448B6CE7FBC922C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " AF Motorsport joined the global St. Patrick's Day celebration with specially designed content blending motorsport imagery with Irish cultural elements. The celebration extended goodwill to fans, partners, and competitors while showcasing the team's personality beyond pure racing content.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The post generated strong engagement across platforms, with the combination of AF Motorsport's distinctive green and navy livery naturally complementing the St. Patrick's Day color palette. Fan responses celebrated the team's community engagement and authentic voice.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	st-patricks-day-2026-celebration	2026-04-10 16:14:24.511+05:30	2026-04-10 16:14:24.511+05:30
9	Pipo Massa First European Victory Celebration	pipo-massa-first-win-celebration	Emotional post-race celebration marking Pipo Massa's breakthrough first European race victory at Barcelona in challenging wet conditions.	private	2026-03-14 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000295C8FC2F5C8444082E2C798BB160240	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The AF Motorsport garage erupted in celebration as Pipo Massa crossed the finish line to secure his first European race victory. The emotional scene saw father Felipe Massa embracing his son, tears visible beneath helmet visors, as the significance of the achievement resonated through the team.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Mechanics who had prepared the Porsche 992 GT3 Cup to perfection shared in the moment, their work validated by the ultimate reward. Engineers who had guided Pipo's development through countless data sessions and simulator hours saw their investment bear fruit on the international stage.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The celebration captured the essence of AF Motorsport's philosophy—that racing is fundamentally about people, relationships, and shared achievement. For Pipo Massa, the victory represented both personal milestone and testament to the support system surrounding him.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	pipo-massa-first-european-victory-celebration	2026-04-10 16:18:03.432+05:30	2026-04-10 16:18:03.432+05:30
10	Father-Son Racing Milestone Barcelona	massa-family-milestone-barcelona	Celebration of the special family milestone as Felipe Massa and his son Pipo compete together under the AF Motorsport banner at Barcelona.	public	2026-03-14 17:30:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000295C8FC2F5C8444082E2C798BB160240	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "A special family milestone captured the attention of the motorsport world as Felipe Massa, Formula 1 vice-champion and veteran of 269 Grand Prix starts, competed alongside his son Pipo Massa in AF Motorsport colors.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The imagery of father and son in matching team wear, sharing the same garage, and debriefing together resonated far beyond the Barcelona paddock. Social media engagement surged as fans worldwide connected with the human story at the heart of professional competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    For AF Motorsport, the Massa family's trust in the team's professional standards and development philosophy provided powerful external validation. The milestone reinforced the organization's reputation as a destination for drivers at all career stages—from emerging talent to established international stars.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	father-son-racing-milestone-barcelona	2026-04-10 16:19:47.888+05:30	2026-04-10 16:19:47.888+05:30
8	Barcelona Post-Weekend Team Appreciation	barcelona-team-appreciation-celebration	Post-weekend recognition gathering celebrating the collective effort of all AF Motorsport personnel during the demanding Barcelona Winter Series finale.	private	2026-03-15 23:30:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000295C8FC2F5C8444082E2C798BB160240	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " As the Barcelona Winter Series weekend concluded, AF Motorsport leadership gathered all team members—drivers, mechanics, engineers, and support staff—to acknowledge outstanding effort and commitment throughout an intense three days of competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The celebration recognized both competitive successes, including Pipo Massa's first European victory, and the resilience demonstrated through challenging moments including Gabriela Correia's repair effort at Murça earlier in the month. The gathering reinforced the team culture that values contribution at every level and understands that championship success is built upon countless individual efforts.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Cold beverages and shared stories capped a weekend that demonstrated AF Motorsport's growing capability and unwavering team spirit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	\N	f	barcelona-post-weekend-team-appreciation	2026-04-14 01:35:27.434+05:30	2026-04-10 16:16:37.859+05:30
\.


