COPY public.championships (id, name, alias, basics_identifiers_code, basics_identifiers_abbreviation, basics_tagline, basics_description, details_history, details_regulations_id, details_format, details_points_system_id, details_standings_scope, details_start_date, details_end_date, details_season_id, details_series_id, details_winner_id, details_runner_up_id, details_third_place_id, details_notes, assets_trophy_id, assets_thumbnail_id, assets_cover_id, assets_video_id, generate_slug, slug, updated_at, created_at) FROM stdin;
4	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica 2026 Rookie Championship	psci-2026-rookie-championship	PSCI-2026-ROOKIE	PSCI R 2026	Emerging Talent Recognition	The Rookie Championship within the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica series recognizes the highest-placed driver competing in their first full season of Porsche Cup competition. The classification encourages new entries to the championship while acknowledging the achievement of adapting successfully to Porsche 992 GT3 Cup machinery.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Rookie Championship was established to support championship growth by recognizing and encouraging new participants. The classification provides additional competitive focus for first-season drivers while creating narrative interest throughout the championship order.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Previous Rookie champions have progressed to front-running overall positions in subsequent seasons, validating the category's role in talent development and championship integration.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	4	Awarded to highest-placed driver in overall championship standings competing in first full Porsche Cup season. Eligibility determined by previous Porsche Cup experience criteria defined in sporting regulations.	5	season_only	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-25 17:00:00+05:30	1	4	1	2	4	Eligibility criteria defined in championship sporting regulations. Previous partial seasons may affect qualification.	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-2026-rookie-championship	2026-04-10 10:36:31.778+05:30	2026-04-09 20:33:18.11+05:30
3	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica 2026 Pro-Am Championship	psci-2026-proam-championship	PSCI-2026-PROAM	PSCI PA 2026	Pro-Am Category Competition	The Pro-Am class within the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship provides categorized competition for Bronze and Silver-graded drivers per FIA driver categorization standards. The class maintains separate points classification while competing concurrently with the overall championship field.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Pro-Am category was introduced to the unified championship in 2024 to provide structured competition for drivers not contesting the overall title. The classification system follows FIA driver categorization protocols, ensuring appropriate competitive grouping while maintaining the integrity of overall championship competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The category has successfully attracted entries from experienced amateur competitors and emerging professional talent, contributing to healthy grid numbers and diverse competition throughout the field.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	4	Same race format as overall championship with separate points classification for Pro-Am eligible drivers. Points awarded per standard scale within category. Overall finishing position also recognized.	5	season_only	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-25 17:00:00+05:30	4	3	2	1	4	Category eligibility determined by FIA driver grading. Subject to championship sporting regulations.	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-2026-pro-am-championship	2026-04-10 10:36:42.651+05:30	2026-04-09 20:31:56.957+05:30
1	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica 2026 Championship	psci-2026-championship	PSCI-2026-CHAMP	PSCI 2026	The Pursuit of Iberian Porsche Supremacy	The 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica overall championship represents the premier title in Iberian one-make GT racing. Contested across six rounds at Portugal and Spain's most prestigious circuits, the championship awards the driver accumulating the highest points total across the season. The title carries significant prestige within the Porsche Motorsport ecosystem and serves as a proven pathway to international Carrera Cup and Supercup opportunities.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The 2026 championship marks the third season of unified Iberian Porsche competition following the successful merger of national Portuguese and Spanish series. The championship has rapidly established itself as a benchmark for professional GT racing in the region, attracting competitive entries from established teams and emerging talent.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The title carries enhanced significance in 2026 with expanded media coverage, increased prize fund, and strengthened connection to Porsche's international motorsport ladder. The champion receives recognition at Porsche Motorsport's annual awards ceremony and priority consideration for Porsche Junior Program evaluation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	1	Six rounds each featuring two 30-minute sprint races. Points awarded to top fifteen finishers per race with bonus points for pole position and fastest lap. Championship classification determined by total points accumulated across all races. Drop scores not applied.	1	season_only	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-25 17:00:00+05:30	1	1	1	2	3	Full 2026 calendar subject to FIA and national federation confirmation. Balance of Performance adjustments may be applied per Porsche Motorsport technical directives.	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-2026-championship	2026-04-10 10:37:16.248+05:30	2026-04-09 20:28:54.256+05:30
2	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica 2025 Championship	psci-2025-championship	PSCI-2025-CHAMP	PSCI 2025	AF Motorsport's Debut Porsche Campaign	The 2025 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship represented AF Motorsport's inaugural season in Porsche one-make competition. The six-round campaign across Portugal and Spain provided the foundation for the team's Porsche program and established competitive benchmarks for future seasons.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The 2025 season marked AF Motorsport's transition to Porsche competition, with the team committing to a full championship campaign in the unified Iberian series. The season represented the culmination of extensive preparation including personnel development, technical partnership establishment, and pre-season testing.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The championship was contested across Estoril, Portimão, Barcelona, and Jerez, with AF Motorsport demonstrating consistent competitiveness from the opening round. The team secured three race victories, six additional podium finishes, and third place in the final championship standings—exceeding pre-season expectations and validating the organization's preparation standards and competitive methodology.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2	Six rounds featuring two 30-minute sprint races per weekend. Points awarded to top fifteen finishers with pole position and fastest lap bonuses. No drop scores applied.	2	season_only	2025-03-22 17:00:00+05:30	2025-10-19 17:00:00+05:30	1	1	1	2	3	AF Motorsport finished third in championship standings. Three victories and nine total podium finishes achieved.	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-2025-championship	2026-04-10 10:37:01.912+05:30	2026-04-09 20:30:42.052+05:30
5	Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica 2026 Team Championship	psci-2026-team-championship	PSCI-2026-TEAM	PSCI Team 2026	Team Excellence Recognition	The Team Championship within the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica series recognizes the most successful entrant organization across the full season. Points are accumulated from all cars entered by a team, rewarding organizations that demonstrate consistent performance across their competitive programs.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Team Championship acknowledges the organizational excellence required to compete successfully in Porsche one-make competition. The classification reflects the combined performance of all team entries, encouraging multi-car programs and recognizing the operational capability required to field competitive entries across an entire season. ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "   For AF Motorsport, the Team Championship provides additional competitive focus and recognition of the organization's preparation standards and operational execution throughout the campaign.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	\N	Team points calculated from the two highest-finishing cars per entrant at each race. Standard points scale applied. Teams may enter additional cars with only highest two scoring toward Team Championship classification.	6	season_only	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-25 17:00:00+05:30	2	2	2	1	4	AF Motorsport targeting top-three Team Championship finish for 2026 season.	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	porsche-sprint-challenge-ibrica-2026-team-championship	2026-04-10 11:05:04.592+05:30	2026-04-09 20:34:24.905+05:30
\.


