3	PSCI Portimão Summer Challenge 2026	psci-portimao-summer-2026	PSCI-2026-R3	The Rollercoaster Awaits	The third round of the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship at Autódromo Internacional do Algarve. Portimão's dramatic elevation changes and challenging layout provide one of the season's most demanding tests, with the circuit's unique character rewarding bravery and precise car control.	Scheduled	Public	3	0101000020E610000012143FC6DC9D4240151DC9E53F4421C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Portimão has rapidly established itself as a driver favorite on the Iberian calendar, with the circuit's undulating profile and blind corners creating a unique challenge unmatched elsewhere in European motorsport. The track demands absolute commitment through the high-speed crests while maintaining precision through the technical final sector.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    For AF Motorsport, Portimão represents a critical championship opportunity. The team's satellite facility at the circuit enables extensive preparation and testing, while the demanding nature of the layout rewards the meticulous setup work that characterizes the team's engineering approach. Strong results at Portimão have historically correlated with championship success.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-06-13 17:00:00+05:30	2026-06-14 17:00:00+05:30	AF Motorsport satellite facility provides operational advantages. Extensive test data available from circuit.	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-portimo-summer-challenge-2026	2026-04-10 10:24:40.061+05:30	2026-04-09 19:52:18.319+05:30
1	PSCI Estoril Season Opener 2026	psci-estoril-opener-2026	PSCI-2026-R1	Home Race Season Launch	The opening round of the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship at AF Motorsport's home circuit, Autódromo do Estoril. This marquee event launches the Iberian Porsche season with two sprint races supporting a comprehensive motorsport program including national championships and historic categories.	Scheduled	Public	1	0101000020E61000001CEBE2361A604340992A1895D4C922C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Estoril has served as the traditional season opener for Portuguese and Iberian Porsche competition, with the circuit's technical demands providing an immediate test of off-season preparation and development. The 2026 opener carries particular significance for AF Motorsport as the team's home event, with extensive partner attendance, media coverage, and the opportunity to establish championship momentum from the first green flag.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The event format follows the championship standard with two 30-minute sprint races across the weekend. The Estoril layout's combination of high-speed commitment through the first sector and technical precision required through the final corners rewards well-prepared cars and confident drivers, typically producing compelling racing throughout the field.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-03-29 17:00:00+05:30	Home event for AF Motorsport. Enhanced partner activation and hospitality program. Track familiarization available Thursday.	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-estoril-season-opener-2026	2026-04-10 10:25:25.268+05:30	2026-04-09 19:48:15.817+05:30
5	PSCI Portimão Autumn Finale 2026	psci-portimao-finale-2026	PSCI-2026-R5	Championship Decider	The fifth and final round of the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship, returning to Autódromo Internacional do Algarve for the season conclusion. The Portimão finale will determine the 2026 champions across all categories, with double points potentially available to maximize championship drama.	Scheduled	Public	5	0101000020E610000012143FC6DC9D4240151DC9E53F4421C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The championship finale returning to Portimão has become tradition for the unified series, with the circuit's challenging nature and overtaking opportunities ensuring championship outcomes remain uncertain until the final laps. The event carries enhanced prestige with championship trophies presented at the circuit's impressive podium facility overlooking the main straight.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The autumn date often brings variable weather conditions to the Algarve, adding strategic complexity to championship-deciding races. Teams must balance championship considerations against competitive instincts, with conservative approaches sometimes yielding to the demands of securing essential points.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-10-24 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-25 17:00:00+05:30	Season finale with championship awards ceremony. Potential for variable autumn weather.	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-portimo-autumn-finale-2026	2026-04-10 10:23:28.504+05:30	2026-04-09 19:58:53.695+05:30
4	PSCI Jerez Midsummer Classic 2026	psci-jerez-midsummer-2026	PSCI-2026-R4	Andalusian Speed Festival	The fourth round of the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship at Circuito de Jerez - Ángel Nieto. The Jerez event represents the championship's second Spanish round, with the circuit's flowing layout and stadium atmosphere creating one of the season's most memorable race weekends.	Scheduled	Public	4	0101000020E6100000DFE00B93A95A42404FAF9465882318C0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jerez's combination of fast, flowing corners and tight, technical sections provides a comprehensive test of vehicle setup and driver adaptability. The circuit's smooth surface and consistent grip levels encourage aggressive driving, while the stadium section's amphitheater setting amplifies the spectator experience and competitive intensity.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The Andalusian climate typically provides stable, warm conditions ideal for consistent performance, though the region's heat can challenge tire management and driver endurance during race distances. The event's midsummer date often positions it as a championship turning point, with title contenders emerging as the season enters its second half.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-07-11 17:00:00+05:30	2026-07-12 17:00:00+05:30	Potential for high ambient and track temperatures requiring enhanced thermal management.	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-jerez-midsummer-classic-2026	2026-04-10 10:23:58.451+05:30	2026-04-09 19:57:22.161+05:30
2	PSCI Barcelona Spring Race 2026	psci-barcelona-spring-2026	PSCI-2026-R2	Championship Continues at Catalunya	The second round of the 2026 Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica championship at Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya. This event marks the championship's first Spanish venue of the season and provides a contrasting challenge to the Estoril opener with Barcelona's flowing layout and emphasis on aerodynamic performance.	Scheduled	Public	2	0101000020E6100000295C8FC2F5C8444082E2C798BB160240	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Barcelona's inclusion on the championship calendar provides teams with data from a circuit extensively used in European motorsport, enabling meaningful performance benchmarking against regional competition. The circuit's balanced layout rewards efficient aerodynamics, strong traction from slow corners, and driver confidence through high-speed direction changes.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The event typically features strong local attendance as Spanish competitors and fans embrace the championship's first domestic round of the season. The professional circuit facilities and extensive runoff areas encourage committed driving, with the long main straight and heavy braking zone into Turn 1 creating the championship's premier overtaking opportunity.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-04-25 17:00:00+05:30	2026-04-26 17:00:00+05:30	First Spanish round of 2026 season. Extensive setup data available from circuit familiarity.	\N	\N	\N	f	psci-barcelona-spring-race-2026	2026-04-10 10:24:59.977+05:30	2026-04-09 19:50:01.002+05:30
6	Rampa Porca de Murça 2026	rampa-porca-de-murca-2026	RPM-2026	Portugal's Ultimate Hillclimb Challenge	The 2026 edition of the legendary Rampa Porca de Murça brings Portugal's premier hillclimb competition to the challenging roads of Murça. AF Motorsport enters with a two-car Porsche lineup featuring André Fernandes in the 991.2 GT3 R making his GT3 R debut and Gabriela Correia in the 991.2 GT3 Cup.	Scheduled	Public	4	0101000020E6100000F9A067B3EAB344401B9E5E29CBD01DC0	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Rampa Porca de Murça continues a tradition of Portuguese hillclimb excellence spanning over three decades. Building upon the memorable 2025 edition, the 2026 event promises intensified competition with AF Motorsport's expanded Porsche program adding GT3 machinery to the traditional hillclimb field.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The event challenges drivers with its combination of technical sections demanding precision and high-speed commitments requiring absolute bravery. The road's memory of past competitions creates an almost mythical quality that drivers reference when describing the Murça experience.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-28 17:00:00+05:30	2026-03-29 17:00:00+05:30	Two-day format with Saturday practice runs and Sunday timed competition. AF Motorsport fielding two Porsche entries. Gabriela Correia making AF Motorsport debut. André Fernandes making GT3 R debut.	\N	\N	\N	f	rampa-porca-de-mura	2026-04-10 15:55:09.525+05:30	2026-04-10 15:54:59.688+05:30
8	Barcelona Winter Series Finale 2026	barcelona-winter-series-finale-2026	GTWS-FINALE-2026	Season Finale at the Catalan Classic	The GT Winter Series concludes its 2026 season at Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya with the championship finale. AF Motorsport fields a significant multi-car entry headlined by the father-son duo of Felipe Massa and Pipo Massa sharing a Porsche 992 GT3 Cup, with additional entries in GT3 and Cup classes.	Completed	Public	2	0101000020E6100000295C8FC2F5C844400000000000000040	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Barcelona Winter Series has established itself as the premier winter competition in European motorsport, attracting international talent and providing essential preparation for the upcoming season. The 2026 edition featured compelling storylines including Felipe Massa's return to competitive GT racing alongside his son Pipo.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The event delivered memorable moments including Pipo Massa's first European victory in wet conditions during Race 1, followed by the adversity of a Race 2 retirement due to contact from another competitor. The weekend demonstrated both the highs and lows inherent in motorsport competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	2026-03-13 17:00:00+05:30	2026-03-15 17:00:00+05:30	Season finale with multiple AF Motorsport entries across classes. Featured first European victory for Pipo Massa. Felipe Massa's return to competitive GT racing generated significant media attention.	\N	\N	93	f	barcelona-winter-series-finale-2026	2026-04-25 18:10:39.041+05:30	2026-04-10 15:56:33.065+05:30
