COPY public.garages (id, name, alias, basics_identifiers_code, basics_tagline, basics_description, details_type, details_capacity, details_size_sq_m, details_accessibility, details_start_date, details_end_date, details_location, details_ownership_id, details_history, details_notes, assets_thumbnail_id, assets_cover_id, generate_slug, slug, updated_at, created_at) FROM stdin;
2	AF Motorsport Portimão Test Facility	afm-portimao-test-facility	AFM-PTF-001	Southern Testing Operations Base	Satellite facility maintained at Autódromo Internacional do Algarve for extended testing programs and southern Portugal operations. This leased garage space provides permanent infrastructure at Portimão, eliminating transport logistics for frequent testing and enabling immediate track access for development programs.\n	Permanent	2	85	Restricted	2024-06-01 17:00:00+05:30	\N	0101000020E6100000D9CEF753E39D42403108AC1C5A4421C0	5	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Portimão satellite facility was established in mid-2024 in response to increased testing demands at the Algarve circuit. Prior to this facility, each Portimão test required complete equipment transport from Estoril, adding signific", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The facility operates on an annual lease arrangement and is utilized approximately twenty days per season for scheduled testing, driver development programs, and pre-event preparation before Portimão race weekends. The location has proven particularly valuable for winter testing when Estoril's climate can be less favorable.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	 Facility shared with partner team under storage agreement. Access coordinated through circuit management. Annual lease renewal June 1.\n	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-portimo-test-facility	2026-04-10 10:29:52.727+05:30	2026-04-09 19:28:38.025+05:30
3	AF Motorsport Karting Base	afm-karting-base	AFM-KB-001	Karting Program Operations Center	Dedicated facility at Estoril Kartódromo supporting AF Motorsport's karting development programs, driver assessments, and corporate karting events. The facility provides kart preparation, storage, and trackside support infrastructure specifically configured for karting operations.	Permanent	6	45	Restricted	2023-09-01 17:00:00+05:30	\N	0101000020E61000000EBE30992A604340D3DEE00B93C922C0	7	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The karting base was established in late 2023 as AF Motorsport formalized its driver development pathway through karting. The facility's location adjacent to the Estoril Kartódromo circuit enables efficient testing and training operations with immediate track access. The base supports the team's fleet of development karts and provides a professional environment for introducing young drivers to structured motorsport preparation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The facility has become an important recruitment tool, allowing prospective drivers and their families to experience AF Motorsport's professional standards and development philosophy in an accessible format. Several current team drivers began their AF Motorsport relationship through assessment days conducted at this facility.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Operates under Kartódromo regulations. Junior driver supervision protocols in place. Facility available for corporate event support.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-karting-base	2026-04-10 10:31:25.443+05:30	2026-04-09 19:28:55.27+05:30
5	AF Motorsport Estoril Workshop	afm-estoril-workshop	AFM-WS-001	Team Headquarters and Primary Operations Center	Main workshop facility located within the Autódromo do Estoril paddock complex serving as AF Motorsport's headquarters, race preparation center, and operational hub. The facility comprises three interconnected garage units totaling 180 square meters of workspace configured for vehicle preparation, engineering operations, parts storage, and team administration. The workshop's location within the circuit provides direct pit lane access and enables efficient testing operations with minimal logistical overhead.	Permanent	4	180	Restricted	2020-03-01 17:00:00+05:30	2026-04-10 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E61000008048BF7D1D604340448B6CE7FBC922C0	7	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Estoril workshop was established in March 2020 as AF Motorsport's first permanent facility, marking the organization's transition from trackside-only operations to a fully professional team structure. The initial configuration comprised a single garage unit with basic preparation capability. Following competitive success and expanded programs, the facility underwent two significant expansions: in 2022, a second adjacent unit was acquired enabling separate preparation areas for primary and development cars; in 2024, a third unit was added to accommodate the expanded Porsche program and simulator installation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	 Workshop operates under Autódromo do Estoril paddock regulations. Access restricted to team personnel and authorized visitors. Noise restrictions apply 22:00-08:00. Annual facility lease renewed December 1.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-estoril-workshop	2026-04-10 10:34:02.041+05:30	2026-04-09 19:31:42.17+05:30
1	AF Motorsport Trackside Garage	afm-trackside-garage	AFM-TS-001	Mobile Race Event Operations	Standardized trackside garage configuration deployed at race events across the Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica calendar and selected international competitions. This mobile operation transforms allocated circuit garage space into a fully functional AF Motorsport preparation facility, maintaining consistent workflow and professional presentation regardless of venue.	Temporary	2	60	Paddock	2024-03-15 17:00:00+05:30	2026-10-31 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	4	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " The trackside garage configuration evolved from the team's early race experiences, with continuous refinement based on operational learnings. The current specification was developed during the 2024 season and standardized for the expanded 2025 Porsche program. Key developments include the custom tool cabinet system that dramatically reduces setup time at new venues and the integrated network architecture that enables seamless communication between trackside and Estoril-based engineering support.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The mobile operation is designed for rapid deployment, with the complete garage package transportable in the team's race transporter alongside the competition vehicles. Setup time from arrival to operational readiness is approximately four hours for a two-person crew. The standardized configuration ensures that drivers and engineers experience consistent working environment and tool locations at every event, reducing cognitive load during high-pressure race weekends.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Configuration adapted per circuit allocation. Supplementary equipment added for endurance events. All equipment inventoried pre and post-event.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-trackside-garage	2026-04-10 11:01:42.069+05:30	2026-04-09 19:28:15.207+05:30
4	AF Motorsport Race Transporter	afm-race-transporter	AFM-TRANS-001	Mobile Team Headquarters	Custom-configured race transporter serving as mobile operations center, vehicle transport, and trackside support hub for AF Motorsport's European competition program. The transporter combines vehicle transport capacity for two Porsche Cup cars with integrated workshop, office, and hospitality functionality, enabling self-sufficient operation at circuits across the Iberian Peninsula and beyond.	Mobile	2	45	Paddock	2024-01-15 17:00:00+05:30	\N	0101000020E6100000448B6CE7FBC922C08048BF7D1D604340	4	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The race transporter was commissioned in early 2024 as part of AF Motorsport's expansion to full European competition capability. The vehicle was specified following extensive analysis of team requirements and circuit logistics, with custom interior configuration completed by Portuguese motorsport vehicle specialists.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The transporter has supported the team's entire Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica campaign, covering approximately 15,000 kilometers annually across Portugal and Spain. The mobile operation capability has proven essential for maintaining consistent preparation standards across varying circuit facilities, with the integrated workshop enabling full service capability regardless of local infrastructure.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Vehicle requires HGV license. ADR regulations apply for fuel transport. Annual technical inspection March. Generator hours logged for service scheduling.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-race-transporter	2026-04-10 10:32:42.906+05:30	2026-04-09 19:28:58.9+05:30
\.


