1	Arai GP-6 RC - André Fernandes 2024 Heritage	arai-gp6-rc-fernandes-2024	2024 Season - First Porsche Campaign	The helmet worn by André Fernandes during his debut Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica campaign in 2024. This helmet holds significant sentimental value as the lid used during the team's transition to Porsche Cup competition and the achievement of AF Motorsport's first podium finishes in the championship. The design represents the team's original visual identity and has been retired from active competition but preserved as part of the team's heritage collection.	Show	Rising Wave	JLF Designs UK	The 2024 design featured a rising wave motif symbolizing the team's ascent into Porsche competition. The design incorporated AF Motorsport's original navy and white color scheme with subtle silver accents. The graphics were intentionally simpler than the current design, reflecting the team's focused, foundational approach to its first Porsche campaign.	#1A2A3A	Prominent	Modern	Glossy	2024-02-10 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	arai-gp-6-rc---andr-fernandes-2024-heritage	2026-04-10 10:37:53.857+05:30	2026-04-09 19:18:50.675+05:30
3	Arai SK-6 - AFM Passenger	arai-sk6-afm-passenger	Passenger Ride Experiences	Arai SK-6 helmet designated for passenger ride experiences, corporate guest hot laps, and media familiarization sessions. The SK-6 offers Arai's renowned protection standards in an accessible, easy-to-fit package suitable for the varying head shapes and sizes encountered with guest passengers. The helmet features Arai's quick-release visor system and comfortable interior suitable for shorter duration use.	Track	Guest Experience	Arai Factory Finish	Simple, professional appearance in AF Motorsport colors designed to photograph well and provide guests with an authentic motorsport experience without the complexity of full custom race helmet preparation.	#1A2A3A	Minimal	Classic	Glossy	2024-06-05 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	arai-sk-6---afm-passenger	2026-04-10 10:38:43.681+05:30	2026-04-09 19:19:20.57+05:30
4	Bell KC7-CMR - AFM Karting Program	bell-kc7-cmr-afm-karting	Karting Development Program	Bell KC7-CMR karting-specific helmet maintained for AF Motorsport's driver development and karting programs. The KC7-CMR is purpose-designed for karting competition, featuring optimized ventilation for the high-exertion environment of kart racing, lightweight carbon composite construction, and a wide aperture for excellent peripheral vision essential in close-quarters karting competition.	Track	Youth Development	Bell Racing Factory	The helmet features Bell's factory competition finish in AF Motorsport colors, providing a professional appearance appropriate for young drivers in development programs. The design is intentionally clean and inspiring for aspiring racers.	#1A2A3A	Prominent	Modern	Glossy	2025-01-20 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	bell-kc7-cmr---afm-karting-program	2026-04-10 10:38:57.429+05:30	2026-04-09 19:19:48.635+05:30
5	Stilo ST6 GT Composite - AFM Team Spare	stilo-st6-gt-afm-spare	Team Spare - Universal Fit Configuration	Stilo ST6 GT Composite helmet maintained as a team spare for driver coaching, passenger rides, and emergency replacement. The ST6 GT offers excellent value within the premium helmet segment, featuring Stilo's composite shell construction and comprehensive ventilation system. This helmet is configured with Stilo's WRC intercom system for seamless integration with the team's communication equipment.	Track	Team Equipment	Stilo Factory Design	The helmet features Stilo's standard competition design with AF Motorsport branding applied via high-quality vinyl graphics. The straightforward aesthetic reflects the helmet's utilitarian role while maintaining professional team appearance standards.	#1A1A1A	Minimal	Modern	Matte	2024-03-10 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	stilo-st6-gt-composite---afm-team-spare	2026-04-10 10:39:17.325+05:30	2026-04-09 19:20:24.088+05:30
2	Arai GP-6 RC - André Fernandes Test	arai-gp6-rc-fernandes-test	Testing and Development Sessions	Secondary Arai GP-6 RC helmet used by André Fernandes for private testing, track days, and development sessions. This helmet provides identical safety performance and comfort to the primary race helmet while preserving the race lid's finish from the inevitable wear associated with frequent use. The simplified design maintains professional appearance while reducing the cost and lead time associated with complex custom paintwork.\n	Track	Clean Technical	Arai Factory Finish	The test helmet employs a clean, technical aesthetic that prioritizes function while maintaining AF Motorsport brand identity. The matte carbon base finish showcases the helmet's construction quality, while minimal team branding in durable vinyl maintains professional appearance without the vulnerability of custom paint during frequent handling.	#2C3E4C	Minimal	Modern	Matte	2024-09-15 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	arai-gp-6-rc---andr-fernandes-test	2026-04-10 10:38:20.44+05:30	2026-04-09 19:19:06.575+05:30
6	Arai GP-6 RC - André Fernandes Primary	arai-gp6-rc-fernandes-primary	Race Day Helmet - Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica	Primary competition helmet worn by André Fernandes during Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica race events. This Arai GP-6 RC represents the pinnacle of Arai's motorsport helmet engineering, featuring the proprietary capping construction that provides exceptional shell strength while maintaining lightweight characteristics. The helmet carries André's signature design scheme developed in collaboration with helmet painter JLF Designs, incorporating AF Motorsport team colors and personal motifs that reflect his Portuguese heritage and racing philosophy.	Track	Portuguese Navigator	JLF Designs UK	The design draws from Portugal's maritime exploration heritage, incorporating compass rose elements and wave motifs rendered in AF Motorsport's signature navy and silver color palette. The gold accents reference Portugal's Age of Discovery while acknowledging achievement and aspiration in motorsport. The design intentionally balances aggressive racing aesthetics with elegant, timeless elements that photograph well and maintain visual impact at speed.	#1A2A3A	Prominent	Modern	Matte	2025-02-01 17:00:00+05:30	\N	\N	\N	f	arai-gp-6-rc---andr-fernandes-primary	2026-04-10 10:39:32.678+05:30	2026-04-09 19:20:32.609+05:30
