3	Portimão VIP Suite Experience 2026	 portimao-vip-suite-2026	HOSP-POR-2026-001	Luxury Hospitality at Portugal's Most Spectacular Circuit	The Portimão VIP Suite Experience delivers premium hospitality at the stunning Autódromo Internacional do Algarve during the Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica summer round. Guests enjoy climate-controlled suite comfort with panoramic circuit views, exceptional catering, and exclusive AF Motorsport team access at one of Europe's most dramatic racing venues.	vip_suite	available	public	30	595	0101000020E61000009A9999999999424000000000008055C0	2026-06-13 14:30:00+05:30	2026-06-14 23:30:00+05:30	2	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Portimão VIP Suite Experience was introduced in 2025 following strong demand for premium hospitality at the Algarve circuit. The unique characteristics of Portimão—dramatic elevation changes, challenging corners, and spectacular vistas—create an exceptional backdrop for VIP hospitality.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    AF Motorsport's suite location provides panoramic views of the circuit's most dramatic sections, while the climate-controlled environment offers welcome relief from the Algarve summer heat. The 2026 experience has been enhanced with additional team integration including extended driver briefings and access to AF Motorsport's satellite facility within the paddock.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Premium suite location with exceptional views of the circuit's signature elevation changes. Weekend packages available including Saturday and Sunday access. Partner and corporate group rates available.	\N	\N	f	portimo-vip-suite-experience-2026	2026-04-10 10:39:02.575+05:30	2026-04-10 09:53:21.172+05:30
1	AF Motorsport Garage Tour and Meet Experience	afm-garage-tour-meet	HOSP-GTM-2026-001	Behind-the-Scenes Access for True Motorsport Enthusiasts	The Garage Tour and Meet Experience provides focused behind-the-scenes access to AF Motorsport's race operations without the full hospitality investment. This experience is ideal for dedicated motorsport enthusiasts seeking authentic insight into professional race team operations and direct interaction with team personnel and drivers.	garage_tour	available	public	15	195	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	2026-03-28 16:30:00+05:30	2026-03-29 21:30:00+05:30	3	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Garage Tour and Meet Experience was developed in response to requests from fans and enthusiasts seeking more accessible engagement with AF Motorsport. The focused format concentrates on the elements guests consistently identify as most valuable: authentic garage access, technical insight, and driver interaction.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The experience has proven particularly popular with young motorsport enthusiasts, amateur competitors, and those considering motorsport career pathways. The smaller group size enables meaningful interaction and personalized attention from team personnel.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Multiple tour times available throughout race weekend. Advance booking recommended as sessions frequently sell out. Custom tours available for corporate or educational groups.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-garage-tour-and-meet-experience	2026-04-10 10:39:54.365+05:30	2026-04-10 09:51:24.008+05:30
5	AF Motorsport Track Walk Experience	afm-track-walk-experience	HOSP-TRACK-2026-001	Walk the Circuit with Professional Racing Drivers	The Track Walk Experience provides a unique opportunity to walk the full Estoril circuit in the company of AF Motorsport drivers and engineers. Participants gain intimate understanding of the challenges and techniques of each corner while experiencing the circuit from the perspective of professional competitors.	track_walk	available	public	25	95	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	2026-03-27 22:30:00+05:30	2026-03-28 00:30:00+05:30	3	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Track Walk Experience was introduced in 2025 following positive feedback from partners who had joined informal circuit walks with team personnel. The structured experience provides deeper insight than typical fan track walks, with professional drivers explaining the specific techniques, reference points, and challenges of each corner.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The experience has proven particularly valuable for amateur drivers, track day enthusiasts, and those seeking to understand the technical aspects of circuit driving. The Thursday evening timing before race weekends allows participants to watch subsequent sessions with enhanced appreciation and understanding.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Thursday evening scheduling allows participants to apply learning to weekend viewing. Private track walks available for corporate groups. Weather-dependent activity with indoor alternative provided if conditions unsafe.	\N	\N	f	af-motorsport-track-walk-experience	2026-04-10 10:37:54.209+05:30	2026-04-10 09:59:07.591+05:30
4	Champagne Celebration Experience	champagne-celebration-experience	HOSP-CHAMP-2026-001	Celebrate AF Motorsport Success in Style	The Champagne Celebration Experience offers the ultimate conclusion to a race weekend—the opportunity to join AF Motorsport's podium celebration should the team achieve a top-three finish. This exclusive experience includes premium hospitality access with the added excitement of participating in the team's celebratory moment.	champagne_celebration	coming_soon	invite_only	10	295	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	2026-03-29 20:30:00+05:30	2026-03-29 22:30:00+05:30	\N	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Champagne Celebration Experience was conceived following the spontaneous and joyous celebrations of AF Motorsport's 2025 victories. Partners and guests who happened to be present for podium finishes described the experience as unforgettable, prompting the creation of a structured experience around these special moments.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    The experience acknowledges the uncertainty inherent in motorsport—celebration cannot be guaranteed—but the anticipation and possibility create their own excitement. Guests who have participated in winning celebrations describe the experience as among their most memorable motorsport moments.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Limited availability due to podium ceremony access restrictions. Experience includes full hospitality regardless of race outcome. Rain check policy applies for cancelled events.	\N	\N	f	champagne-celebration-experience	2026-04-10 10:38:40.725+05:30	2026-04-10 09:57:07.061+05:30
2	Estoril Paddock Club Experience 2026	estoril-paddock-club-2026	HOSP-EST-2026-001	Premium Race Weekend Hospitality at AF Motorsport's Home Circuit	The Estoril Paddock Club Experience offers the ultimate VIP hospitality package for the Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica season opener at Autódromo do Estoril. Guests enjoy premium trackside viewing, gourmet catering, exclusive team access, and behind-the-scenes experiences with AF Motorsport personnel throughout the race weekend. This comprehensive hospitality package provides an immersive motorsport experience at Portugal's most historic racing circuit.	paddock_club	available	public	40	495	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	2026-03-28 14:30:00+05:30	2026-03-29 23:30:00+05:30	2	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Estoril Paddock Club was introduced for the 2025 season opener and quickly established itself as AF Motorsport's premier hospitality offering. The inaugural event sold out within two weeks of announcement, with exceptional guest feedback highlighting the authentic team access and professional hospitality standards.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Limited capacity of 40 guests per day. Early booking recommended as 2025 event sold out completely. Group discounts available for parties of 6 or more. Corporate branding opportunities available for partners.	\N	\N	f	estoril-paddock-club-experience-2026	2026-04-10 10:39:25.42+05:30	2026-04-10 09:51:36.555+05:30
\.


