5	Estoril Youth Motorsport Engagement 2026	estoril-youth-engagement-2026	Inspiring the Next Generation of Motorsport Enthusiasts	To introduce young people from the Cascais and greater Lisb	The Estoril Youth Motorsport Engagement Program partners with local schools and youth organizations to provide structured motorsport exposure for young people aged 12 to 18. The program includes circuit visits, career awareness sessions, and introductory karting experiences designed to broaden awareness of motorsport opportunities.	2026-03-01 17:00:00+05:30	2026-11-30 17:00:00+05:30	0101000020E6100000992A1895D4C922C01CEBE2361A604340	\N	\N	\N	f	estoril-youth-motorsport-engagement-2026	2026-04-10 10:36:13.596+05:30	2026-04-10 09:29:53.666+05:30
