2	Ricardo	Jorge	Santos	ricardo-santosRick	Rick	Sporting Director	Male	4	1982-11-12 17:00:00+05:30	2021-06-01 17:00:00+05:30	\N	To establish AF Motorsport's trackside operations as the most professional and effective in Iberian Porsche competition, providing drivers with optimal conditions for performance.	Direct all trackside and competitive operations including race strategy, sporting regulation compliance, and driver management during events.	Calm minds make fast decisions.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ricardo Santos joined AF Motorsport in 2021 as Sporting Director, bringing extensive experience from national and international motorsport competition. His background includes race engineering roles in Portuguese GT championships and operational management positions with event organizing bodies.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    As Sporting Director, Ricardo oversees all trackside operations during race events including strategy formulation, pit wall communications, and regulatory compliance. His calm demeanor and methodical approach provide stability during high-pressure competitive situations.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Ricardo's comprehensive understanding of sporting regulations across multiple championships ensures AF Motorsport maximizes competitive opportunity within regulatory frameworks while maintaining exemplary compliance standards.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Prior to joining AF Motorsport, Ricardo served as race engineer for Portuguese GT teams and held operational roles with national championship organizers. This dual perspective provides valuable insight into both competitive and regulatory aspects of motorsport.\n    \n    Ricardo's approach to sporting direction emphasizes preparation and clear communication. Race strategies are developed collaboratively with drivers and engineers, with contingencies established for likely scenarios. This preparation enables decisive execution when split-second decisions are required.	\N	\N	t	\N	2026-04-10 10:27:43.252+05:30	2026-04-09 20:47:58.664+05:30
1	André	Miguel	Fernandes	andre-fernandes	AF	Team Principal and Founder	Male	238	1995-08-15 17:00:00+05:30	2020-03-01 17:00:00+05:30	\N	To establish AF Motorsport as the benchmark for professional independent motorsport organizations in Iberia, demonstrating that meticulous preparation, driver development focus, and commercial professionalism can achieve sustained competitive success.	Lead AF Motorsport's competitive and commercial development while maintaining active driving role. Build organizational capability through strategic partnerships, personnel development, and operational excellence.	Performance through preparation. Speed through precision.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "André Fernandes founded AF Motorsport in 2020, transitioning from successful national competitor to team principal while maintaining an active driving career. His dual role combines organizational leadership with direct competitive involvement, providing unique perspective on all aspects of team operations.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Under André's leadership, AF Motorsport has developed from trackside-only operations to a fully professional organization with permanent Estoril facilities, multi-car Porsche program, and comprehensive driver development pathway. The team's competitive achievements include multiple race victories and championship podiums in Porsche Sprint Challenge Ibérica competition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    André's leadership philosophy emphasizes continuous improvement, attention to detail, and the development of people as the foundation of sustained competitive success. This approach has cultivated strong relationships with technical partners, commercial sponsors, and the broader motorsport community.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Prior to founding AF Motorsport, André Fernandes competed successfully in Portuguese national championships including touring car and GT categories. This competitive experience informed the operational standards and preparation philosophy that define AF Motorsport's approach.\n    \n    The decision to establish a professional team organization reflected recognition that sustained competitive success requires excellence across all operational dimensions. The Estoril workshop facility, technical partnerships, and personnel development programs were established to create the infrastructure necessary for long-term achievement.\n    \n    The transition to Porsche competition in 2025 represented the culmination of this developmental approach, with AF Motorsport immediately demonstrating competitiveness at the Iberian championship level.	\N	\N	t	\N	2026-04-27 22:51:28.335+05:30	2026-04-09 20:45:42.929+05:30
4	Sofia	Isabel	Martins	sofia-martins	Sof	Commercial Director	Female	15	1989-09-18 17:00:00+05:30	2023-01-10 17:00:00+05:30	\N	vision: To establish AF Motorsport as the premier commercial platform in Iberian motorsport, delivering exceptional value to partners while building sustainable organizational growth.	Lead all commercial operations including partnership development, sponsor activation, hospitality programs, and brand strategy. Cultivate long-term relationships that benefit both team and partners.	Partnerships built on value endure beyond results.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Sofia Martins leads AF Motorsport's commercial operations, bringing extensive experience in sports marketing and partnership development from previous roles with Portuguese sports organizations and agencies.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "As Commercial Director, Sofia manages the complete partnership lifecycle from initial engagement through activation and renewal. Her strategic approach focuses on understanding partner objectives and delivering measurable value through authentic motorsport engagement.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Sofia's leadership has professionalized AF Motorsport's commercial operations, establishing systems and processes that enable sustainable growth and professional partner relationships.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	  Sofia's background includes commercial roles with Portuguese Olympic Committee partners and sports marketing agencies serving major Portuguese brands. This experience informs her understanding of partnership dynamics and value creation.\n    \n    Since joining AF Motorsport, Sofia has developed the commercial infrastructure including partnership packages, activation programs, and reporting systems that demonstrate return on investment. Her work has attracted and retained partners essential to the team's growth.	\N	\N	f	sofia-martins	2026-04-10 10:26:47.098+05:30	2026-04-09 20:56:55.104+05:30
3	Miguel	Ângelo	Costa	Mig	Mig	Technical Director	Male	8	1985-04-23 17:00:00+05:30	2022-02-15 17:00:00+05:30	2026-04-16 17:00:00+05:30	To develop AF Motorsport's technical capability to championship-winning standard through systematic improvement, knowledge capture, and engineering excellence.	Lead all technical operations including vehicle preparation, setup development, data analysis, and performance optimization. Manage engineering personnel and technical partnerships.	Data informs. Understanding decides.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Miguel Costa leads AF Motorsport's technical operations, overseeing vehicle preparation, engineering methodology, and performance development. His background combines formal engineering education with extensive practical motorsport experience.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    As Technical Director, Miguel manages the engineering team, technical partnerships, and the continuous development of AF Motorsport's technical capability. His systematic approach to setup development and performance optimization has been fundamental to the team's competitive progression.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "    Miguel's leadership has established the data-driven methodology that characterizes AF Motorsport's engineering approach, balancing analytical rigor with the practical realities of trackside operation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	Miguel's motorsport career began in karting before transitioning to engineering roles in national formula car championships. His experience spans single-seaters, touring cars, and GT racing, providing broad technical perspective.\n    \n    Since joining AF Motorsport, Miguel has developed the technical infrastructure including data acquisition systems, setup methodologies, and engineering processes. His work has been instrumental in the team's successful transition to Porsche competition.	\N	\N	t	\N	2026-04-10 10:27:17.104+05:30	2026-04-09 20:50:18.354+05:30
\.


