COPY public.leaders_details_principles_list (_order, _parent_id, id, name, description, statement, application, rationale) FROM stdin;
1	4	69d7c4b1bc5c815571baa439	Authentic Value Creates Lasting Partnerships	Successful commercial relationships are built on genuine value exchange rather than transactional arrangements.	We don't sell logo placement. We create meaningful connections between partners and the motorsport community.	Partnership programs tailored to partner objectives with measurable outcomes and transparent reporting.	Sustainable commercial growth requires relationships that benefit all parties beyond immediate financial exchange.
1	3	69d7c379bc5c815571baa438	Data Informs, Instinct Executes	Analytical rigor provides the foundation for informed decision-making. Ultimately, racing demands human judgment applied to complex situations.	We embrace data without surrendering to it. Telemetry guides us; it does not drive for us.	Comprehensive data analysis informs setup direction and driver development. Final decisions incorporate driver feedback and competitive context.	Optimal performance emerges from the synthesis of analytical understanding and human judgment.
1	2	69d7c30fbc5c815571baa437	Preparation Enables Decisive Action	Effective race strategy requires comprehensive pre-event preparation. Decisions made under pressure are only as good as the analysis supporting them.	We make our difficult decisions before the race starts. What remains is execution.	Detailed pre-event strategy sessions covering all likely scenarios. Clear decision protocols established before arriving at circuit.	Race conditions demand rapid decisions. Preparation ensures those decisions are informed rather than reactive.
1	1	69d7c240bc5c815571baa432	Preparation Precedes Performance	Competitive outcomes are determined long before lights out. Victory is forged in workshop preparation, engineering analysis, and simulator sessions.	We never confuse effort with effectiveness. Every hour of preparation must translate to measurable competitive advantage.	All team operations from vehicle preparation to driver development follow documented procedures ensuring consistent quality and continuous improvement.	Motorsport success correlates directly with preparation quality. Teams that prepare thoroughly create conditions for performance to emerge.
2	1	69d7c25cbc5c815571baa433	People Development Drives Progress	Organizational capability is built through investment in people. Developing talent at all levels creates sustainable competitive advantage.	We measure success not solely through silverware but through careers launched, skills developed, and potential realized.	Structured development programs for drivers, mechanics, and engineers with clear progression pathways and mentorship support.	Motorsport organizations ultimately succeed or fail based on the quality and commitment of their people.
\.


