5	Welcome to AF Motorsport - Intro Slide	welcome-intro	SLD-INTRO-001	Opening introduction slide for AF Motorsport presentations establishing brand identity, core values, and presentation context. Used as the lead-in for partner presentations, driver briefings, and stakeholder updates.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "AF Motorsport", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	intro	landscape	corporate	fade	8	1	Present with confident, measured delivery. Allow brand mark to establish presence before speaking. This slide sets the professional tone for everything that follows.	Ensure consistent use across all presentation decks. Fonts, colors, and spacing must match brand guidelines exactly.	\N	\N	\N	f	welcome-to-af-motorsport---intro-slide	2026-04-10 10:42:27.725+05:30	2026-04-09 19:02:47.213+05:30
4	Partnership Value Proposition	partnership-value-proposition	SLD-PART-001	Strategic slide articulating the commercial value and activation opportunities available to AF Motorsport partners. Core component of sponsorship proposals and partnership renewal presentations.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Partnership Value", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "AF Motorsport partnerships deliver measurable business outcomes through authentic motorsport engagement, targeted audience reach, and premium hospitality experiences.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	highlight	landscape	corporate	slide	30	4	Focus on ROI metrics and activation examples. Partners want to understand tangible benefits, not just logo placement. Use specific case studies where possible.	Include activation imagery showing partner branding on cars, team wear, and at events. Visual proof of exposure matters.	\N	\N	\N	f	partnership-value-proposition	2026-04-10 10:43:28.135+05:30	2026-04-09 19:02:17.849+05:30
2	Team Overview - Who We Are	team-overview	SLD-OV-002	Comprehensive team overview slide presenting AF Motorsport's structure, key personnel, operational capabilities, and competitive history. Essential for first-time partner meetings and stakeholder orientations.	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Who We Are", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "AF Motorsport is an Estoril-based professional racing organization competing in premier Iberian and European championships. Founded on principles of engineering excellence and driver development, we combine Portuguese racing heritage with modern motorsport methodology.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}	overview	landscape	corporate	slide	20	2	Emphasize three key pillars: Technical Excellence, Driver Development, Commercial Professionalism. Use this slide to establish credibility with new audiences.	Update with current season statistics and personnel changes before each presentation.	\N	\N	\N	f	team-overview---who-we-are	2026-04-10 10:44:15.11+05:30	2026-04-09 19:01:33.454+05:30
\.


